\taxon{Definition}
\title{Lenses and charts}
\p{
  Let #{\cA: \cC^\op \to \Cat} be an indexed category. A \em{chart} is simply a morphism in the Grothendieck construction #{\int \cA}. A \em{lens} is a morphism in the fiberwise opposite #{\int \cA(-)^\op}.
}